import React, { useState } from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import { Input } from "../../component/ui/input"; import { Button } from "../../component/ui/button"; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; const URI = "http://localhost:8000/usuarios/" const CreacteUser = () => { const [Name, setName] = useState(' ') const [last_name, setLastName] = useState(' ') const [user, setUser] = useState(' ') const [email, setEmail] = useState(' ') const [password, setPassword] = useState('') const [tel, setTel] = useState(' ') const [andress, setAndress] = useState(' ') const navigate = useNavigate() const createUser = async (e) => { e.preventDefault() console.log( Name + last_name ) await axios.post(URI, { Name: Name, lastName: last_name, user: user, email: email, password: password, tel: tel, andress: andress }) navigate('/') } return(<>
setName(e.target.value) } id="nameP" type="text" placeholder="Nombre" value={ Name }>
setLastName(e.target.value) } id="nameL" type="text" placeholder="Apellido" value={ last_name }>
setUser(e.target.value) } id="User" type="text" placeholder="Usuario" value={ user }>
setEmail(e.target.value) } id="email" type="text" placeholder="Email" value={ email }>
setPassword(e.target.value) } id="password" type="text" placeholder="password" value={ email }>
setTel(e.target.value) } id="tel" type="num" placeholder="Tel" value={ tel }>
setAndress(e.target.value) } id="andress" type="text" placeholder="Dirección" value={ andress }>
) } export default CreacteUser
